Package: fastroll
Type: Package
Title: Fast Rolling Window Statistics
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-06-12
Authors@R: person("bagol1000", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "01199218@pw.edu.pl")
Description: High-performance rolling window statistics including basic
    moments, minima and maxima, linear regression, covariance, Pearson and
    Spearman correlation, correlation matrices, quantiles, and expanding
    windows backed by a shared 'C++17' core with 'OpenMP' support.  The
    same core is published for 'Python' as the 'fastwindow' package.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/bagol1000/fastwindow
BugReports: https://github.com/bagol1000/fastwindow/issues
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.10)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0)
SystemRequirements: C++17, OpenMP
Encoding: UTF-8
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
